Citations
Date: 0/0/1988
Source: Dictionary of Kiwi Slang, A
Author: McGILL
Vol / Page: 125
Edition:
Quote: <i>would you rather walk a mile and climb a stile or eat a sunburned cake?</i> (cowpat) question for somebody objecting to walking, usually asked by parent of a child in grave danger of being left behind among the cowpats.
